@startuml public-widget-conversation
title Public Widget Conversation and Ticket Creation

hide footbox

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 16
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #111111
  LifeLineBorderColor #111111
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantBorderColor #111111
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantFontColor #111111
  ParticipantFontSize 16
  ActorBorderColor #111111
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ActorFontSize 16
  GroupBorderColor #111111
  GroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}

actor "Visitor" as Visitor
participant "Widget UI" as UI
participant "Routes +\nValidation" as Routes
participant "WidgetPublic\nController" as Controller
participant "WidgetPublic\nService" as PublicService
participant "FileService" as FileService
participant "Domain Models\nWidget/Session/File/Contact/Ticket" as Models
participant "TicketService" as TicketService
participant "MessageService" as MessageService
participant "RealtimePublisher" as Realtime

== 1. Bootstrap/session ==

UI -> Routes: GET bootstrap
Routes -> Controller: validated request
Controller -> PublicService: load public bootstrap
PublicService -> Models: active widget + active mailbox
PublicService --> UI: widget config + realtime metadata

UI -> Routes: POST session
Routes -> Controller: validated request
Controller -> PublicService: start or resume session
PublicService -> Models: create/resume wgs_* session\nand load conversation snapshot
PublicService --> UI: session token + conversation

== 2. Optional attachment upload ==

opt Attachment before message
  Visitor -> UI: Select file
  UI -> Routes: POST files
  Routes -> Controller: parsed file + validated sessionToken
  Controller -> PublicService: upload widget file
  PublicService -> FileService: verify session, upload with\nwidget/session metadata
  FileService -> Models: enforce limits, store object,\ncreate ready file
  FileService --> UI: file id
end

== 3. Send message ==

Visitor -> UI: Sends message
UI -> Routes: POST messages
Routes -> Controller: validated message + attachment ids
Controller -> PublicService: create public widget message
PublicService -> Models: verify session, attachments,\ncontact/identity, current ticket

== 4. Reuse/create ticket ==

alt Reuse current non-closed same-mailbox ticket
  PublicService -> MessageService: append customer_message
  MessageService -> Models: persist message, link attachments,\nupdate ticket/conversation
  MessageService -> Realtime: publish message + conversation events
else Create new widget ticket
  PublicService -> TicketService: create widget ticket\nwith initial customer_message
  TicketService -> Models: create ticket, conversation,\nmessage, attachment links
  TicketService -> Realtime: publish ticket + message events
end

== 5. Sync response/realtime ==

PublicService -> Models: sync session pointers
PublicService --> UI: message + conversation + session

@enduml
